We may store or transfer some or all of your personal data in countries that are not part of the European Economic Area (the “EEA” consists of all EU member states, plus Norway, Iceland, and Liechtenstein). We will take additional steps in order to ensure that your personal data is treated just as safely and securely as it would be within the Channel Islands and UK.
5. Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or Personal Information that we hold about you, including any requests to exercise your rights, please contact us using the details set out below:
